  "detailed_description": "<h1>ADD FULL GAME TO YOUR WISHLIST</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>This is the free prologue to <strong><i>Cult Of Babel</i></strong> - A roguelite Horde Survivors with dungeon crawling elements. This Prologue lets you access the first area of the game. Select your mighty steampunk witch or wizard, get the ancient cards of power and slaughter the horde of evil cultists guarding the tower of babel.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/4edfa82633df56f1ef89eccac2a0f788.webp?t=1664130969\" width=620 height=63 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast-paced horde survival gameplay<br></li><li>Play as one of the legendary sorcerers<br></li><li>Get magic cards to upgrade your steampunk wizard's arsenal<br></li><li>Zany Synergies<br></li><li>Quick, 15 min sessions for quick fun</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/8d28f97732e3659f4c74f569119f45ff.avif?t=1664130969\" width=620 height=126 /></span><br><br>In this roguelite, arena survival game, the randomized cards you get change how you play the game completely. Become a thunder mage, control gravity and much more !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/500feb592e51de13daeb2b873a321269.poster.avif?t=1664130969\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/500feb592e51de13daeb2b873a321269.webm?t=1664130969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/500feb592e51de13daeb2b873a321269.mp4?t=1664130969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/faeb054aa16aa503bbf09da726f2fcdd.avif?t=1664130969\" width=620 height=119 /></span><br><br>60+ cards to collect and upgrade ! The more cards you have in your deck, the more their effects combine and enable you to unleash the fury of ancient magic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/8c3f62b84d367e0c43dc9b61c92781d2.avif?t=1664130969\" width=620 height=153 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/bc19d935b33716dbdec68f13d0eb74c2.poster.avif?t=1664130969\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/bc19d935b33716dbdec68f13d0eb74c2.webm?t=1664130969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/bc19d935b33716dbdec68f13d0eb74c2.mp4?t=1664130969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/21a3b64951b9057ce5c2ff04e26f3860.poster.avif?t=1664130969\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/21a3b64951b9057ce5c2ff04e26f3860.webm?t=1664130969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/21a3b64951b9057ce5c2ff04e26f3860.mp4?t=1664130969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/9b2043176d3af68d7298200580d4a0cb.avif?t=1664130969\" width=620 height=119 /></span><br><br>Play as one of the legendary sorcerers ! There are many characters to choose from each run.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/267e77f437aa0df659a8b6eb2f42a143.webp?t=1664130969\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/267e77f437aa0df659a8b6eb2f42a143.poster.avif?t=1664130969\" class=\"bb_img\" width=620 height=360 /></picture></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2101600/extras/2b8a3372e83c78c667f9d948369b2395.avif?t=1664130969\" width=620 height=163 /></span><br><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New characters to unlock, each with their own weapon and ability<br></li><li>New areas to explore<br></li><li>New map variations<br></li><li>New booster packs and build diversity<br></li><li><strong>Dungeon-crawling !</strong> You'll be able to <strong>climb through the levels</strong> and fight the boss of the cult at the top of the tower</li></ul>",
